title: Durianrider: Threats, Lies, Videotape.
description:
(1) If you don't know where the story starts (or what the criminal charges now unfolding are all about), click through to this three-minute video that shows Durianrider's threats-of-violence and defamatory statements against me:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CRLbgCzJHyM
(2) Here is the link to the anonymous video: "Durianrider - Who do you think is lying?" (the original video is several minutes longer than the version I've presented here).
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KGydEcf1rNs
(3) Here's a link to "the Veg Bro", who appears for about five seconds toward the end of the video ("I love freedom of speech…").
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCTAY8JvB-icDcn83FI6gQ9g/videos
(4) The woman quoted as giving her expert opinion (on the couch) is apparently Kati Morton, a licensed therapist active on youtube:
https://www.youtube.com/user/KatiMorton/videos
